    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "REPUBLIC. Wash. Jan. 24.-The\ncoke supply at the CRANKY smelter is\nagain reported to be short and until\nthis can be adjusted the demand for\nRepublic ores will be limited. The\nprogress of the Lone Pine mine has\nbeen most satisfactory. but for a\ntime the working force has been cut\ndown to four men."
    }
  ]
